The Telegraph - Calcutta
 Santosh Trophy from October 14
Margao: The national football championship for the Santosh Trophy will be held in Kochi from October 14-31. Bangalore will host the Federation Cup from November 20-30, the AIFF executive committee meeting decided in New Delhi on Thursday. It was also decided that the clubs will be allowed to register three foreigners and field three in the National League and the Federation Cup. For all other domestic tournaments, three foreign players can be registered and two can play. Earlier, ruled permitted registering four foreigners for the National League.  (PTI)  Copyright 
